{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>HTTP Cookie（也叫Web cookie或者浏览器Cookie）是服务器发送到用户浏览器并保存在浏览器上的一块数据，它会在浏览器下一次发起请求时被携带并发送到服务器上。</p>\n<h2 id=\"cookie主要用在以下三个方面\"><a href=\"#cookie%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cookie主要用在以下三个方面:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>会话状态管理（如用户登录状态、购物车、游戏分数和其它需要记录的信息）</li>\n<li>个性化设置（如用户自定义设置、主题等）</li>\n<li>浏览器行为跟踪（如跟踪分析用户行为）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Cookie曾一度用于客户端数据的存储，当时没有其它合适的存储办法而作为唯一的存储手段，但随着现在浏览器开始支持各种各样的存储方式而逐渐被废弃。</p>\n<h2 id=\"创建cookie\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BAcookie\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>创建Cookie</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/dist/latest-v8.x/docs/api/http.html#http_response_setheader_name_value\">node</a></p>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"HTTP Cookie（也叫Web cookie或者浏览器Cookie）是服务器发送到用户浏览器并保存在浏览器上的一块数据，它会在浏览器下一次发起请求时被携带并发送到服务器上。 Cookie…","frontmatter":{"title":"cookie","cover":null,"date":"2017-02-15T22:00:01.000Z","category":"JavaScript","tags":["cookie"]},"fields":{"nextTitle":"keyboard","nextSlug":"/javascript/keybord/","prevTitle":"改变keyboard 显示样式","prevSlug":"/javascript/change-search-text-in--keyboard/","slug":"/javascript/cookie/","date":"2017-02-14T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/javascript/cookie/"}}